{"tid":8474,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[金光布袋戲]仲有無人有睇東皇戰影","createTime":"2016-11-28T11:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T13:58:10.000Z","uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71369e91f1a2e9d9540fa01d74ddac0e3ff91a83","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"有無同好仲有睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cd808b1d6247ae9e452490b8599a0c5f64b64d","tid":8474,"uid":18545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"想睇番成套大儒俠史豔文"},{"pid":"7b74bd9765d33e97dac45b6667fa89a2f2ff857e","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇番成套大儒俠史豔文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有2000年個套既台語中字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d3e8e4014efb520753c171243025437b43706e","tid":8474,"uid":18545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"正喎，其實去到中段多左個金剛出來就沒睇，可以劇透一下之後係點呢？"},{"pid":"fab8a55fcfc1822356c3d86b38a413f9776056a1","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正喎，其實去到中段多左個金剛出來就沒睇，可以劇透一下之後係點呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講小金剛，定係大個隻先，如果係大個隻之後除左佢仲有多兩隻嫁，後尾好似都死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28772bb3bdd7c2534dd3b8419eb08b7d6dfcb7c3","tid":8474,"uid":21808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無同好仲有睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有，龍子智商好撚廢表現唔到代掌師相既能力，完全比宵王屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劍無極換新偶等睇佢帶領東劍道擔大旗！會唔會又比殘忍聯盟軍師玩弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ed0083267da6ea8a663e0a7f6dec630339f5a5","tid":8474,"uid":6557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"海境好撚悶，以俏如來智商都俾人係海境搞咁耐，根本就拖劇情"},{"pid":"c4bab7f12a7ad91b813c901d47a2c680b6f0999d","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無同好仲有睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有，龍子智商好撚廢表現唔到代掌師相既能力，完全比宵王屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劍無極換新偶等睇佢帶領東劍道擔大旗！會唔會又比殘忍聯盟軍師玩弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n龍子原全無表現過佢係有智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一味看到鬼"},{"pid":"50c840d41debb1e57718b709c9ba9b5f9e3e19c8","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海境好撚悶，以俏如來智商都俾人係海境搞咁耐，根本就拖劇情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次睇巴哈個面講係換左編劇，唔係三弦黎，所以下滑左唔少<br />\n堂堂鉅子變弱智"},{"pid":"bc255eb7f530ccb357790ed6c79da09988b40467","tid":8474,"uid":3074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海境好撚悶，以俏如來智商都俾人係海境搞咁耐，根本就拖劇情</blockquote><br />\n<br 